 &lt;iframe allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share; fullscreen" loading="eager" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/1Dy48-Bl04U?autoplay=0&amp;amp;controls=1&amp;amp;end=0&amp;amp;loop=0&amp;amp;mute=0&amp;amp;start=0" style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border:0;" title="YouTube video">&lt;/iframe>
 &lt;/div>

&lt;p>這支影片分享我使用「得到 GetSeed 錄音卡」兩個多月後的實際心得。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>從 2026 年 3 月 5 日開箱使用，到 2026 年 5 月 21 日為止，我已經累積了 672 條錄音。這些錄音長短不一，有的是幾分鐘的散步口述，有的是一整節課的上課錄音，也有會議、看診、閒聊、影片拍攝前的口述準備。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>20260520自由人生實驗室#010：愈認真，你就愈陷入這個停不了的遊戲裡。</title><link>https://garrolan.github.io/garrosolivagant/videos/20260520-010-course-evaluation-red-queen/</link><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 00:10:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://garrolan.github.io/garrosolivagant/videos/20260520-010-course-evaluation-red-queen/</guid><description>&lt;div style="position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden;">
 &lt;iframe allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share; fullscreen" loading="eager" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/MfgSVvxoYs4?autoplay=0&amp;amp;controls=1&amp;amp;end=0&amp;amp;loop=0&amp;amp;mute=0&amp;amp;start=0" style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border:0;" title="YouTube video">&lt;/iframe>
 &lt;/div>

&lt;p>這是自由人生實驗室第 10 支影片。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>原本今天想拍別的主題，但下午參加完學校的課程評鑑活動後，心情有點煩躁，於是臨時改成記錄當下的職場情緒與思考。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>20260520自由人生實驗室#009：生活就是一場小實驗</title><link>https://garrolan.github.io/garrosolivagant/videos/20260520-009-life-as-small-experiment/</link><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 00:09:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://garrolan.github.io/garrosolivagant/videos/20260520-009-life-as-small-experiment/</guid><description>&lt;div style="position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden;">
 &lt;iframe allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share; fullscreen" loading="eager" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9B7ulM-leKM?autoplay=0&amp;amp;controls=1&amp;amp;end=0&amp;amp;loop=0&amp;amp;mute=0&amp;amp;start=0" style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border:0;" title="YouTube video">&lt;/iframe>
 &lt;/div>

&lt;p>這是自由人生實驗室第 9 支影片，主題是「生活就是一場小實驗」。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>這次從「自由人生實驗室」的命名由來談起：我想探討讓人生變得更自由的做法、經驗與感受，但不想用成功人士或人生導師的姿態來指導別人。比起給出標準答案，我更想記錄自己真正經歷過的事情，以及在生活裡慢慢測試出來的體會。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>20260519自由人生實驗室#008：低流量也繼續拍攝影片的3個理由</title><link>https://garrolan.github.io/garrosolivagant/videos/20260519-008-mic-test-low-traffic-creation/</link><pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 00:08:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://garrolan.github.io/garrosolivagant/videos/20260519-008-mic-test-low-traffic-creation/</guid><description>&lt;div style="position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden;">
 &lt;iframe allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share; fullscreen" loading="eager" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BCty8Nda2WY?autoplay=0&amp;amp;controls=1&amp;amp;end=0&amp;amp;loop=0&amp;amp;mute=0&amp;amp;start=0" style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border:0;" title="YouTube video">&lt;/iframe>
 &lt;/div>

&lt;p>這是自由人生實驗室的第 8 支影片，也是一支新領夾麥克風的實測影片。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>表面上是在測試收音設備，實際上更想聊的是：如果影片幾乎沒有流量、也不太可能爆紅，那我為什麼還要繼續拍？&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>20260518自由人生實驗室#007：把一天拿回來：我的生活主權時間管理</title><link>https://garrolan.github.io/garrosolivagant/videos/20260518-007-time-sovereignty-management/</link><pubDate>Mon, 18 May 2026 00:07:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://garrolan.github.io/garrosolivagant/videos/20260518-007-time-sovereignty-management/</guid><description>&lt;div style="position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden;">
 &lt;iframe allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share; fullscreen" loading="eager" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9Yhdtr44EYs?autoplay=0&amp;amp;controls=1&amp;amp;end=0&amp;amp;loop=0&amp;amp;mute=0&amp;amp;start=0" style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border:0;" title="YouTube video">&lt;/iframe>
 &lt;/div>

&lt;p>這是自由人生實驗室的一期影片，分享我對「時間管理」的個人理解與實踐。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>這次不是要介紹一套萬用方法，也不是要追求極致效率，而是從自己的生活經驗出發，思考：什麼樣的時間管理，才真的適合我？&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>20260517自由人生實驗室#006：自律真的能夠帶來自由嗎？</title><link>https://garrolan.github.io/garrosolivagant/videos/20260517-006-discipline-and-freedom/</link><pubDate>Sun, 17 May 2026 00:06:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://garrolan.github.io/garrosolivagant/videos/20260517-006-discipline-and-freedom/</guid><description>&lt;div style="position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden;">
 &lt;iframe allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share; fullscreen" loading="eager" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6d4aPa0TNlE?autoplay=0&amp;amp;controls=1&amp;amp;end=0&amp;amp;loop=0&amp;amp;mute=0&amp;amp;start=0" style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border:0;" title="YouTube video">&lt;/iframe>
 &lt;/div>

&lt;p>這支影片想討論一個問題：自律真的能夠帶來自由嗎？&lt;/p>
&lt;p>我以前也很喜歡個人成長、自律、打卡、閱讀量、任務清單這些方法，但慢慢發現，自律如果變成唯一目標，也可能讓人被指標綁架，甚至忘記自己真正想過的是什麼樣的生活。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>20260515自由人生實驗室#005：清晨散步～可持續運動與創作方式測試</title><link>https://garrolan.github.io/garrosolivagant/videos/20260515-005-morning-walk-creative-test/</link><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 00:05:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://garrolan.github.io/garrosolivagant/videos/20260515-005-morning-walk-creative-test/</guid><description>&lt;div style="position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden;">
 &lt;iframe allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share; fullscreen" loading="eager" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/_ZjcqH2nn_0?autoplay=0&amp;amp;controls=1&amp;amp;end=0&amp;amp;loop=0&amp;amp;mute=0&amp;amp;start=0" style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border:0;" title="YouTube video">&lt;/iframe>
 &lt;/div>

&lt;p>這支影片是自由人生實驗室的一次清晨散步紀錄。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>我在早晨散步時，順便測試 Insta360 GO 2 運動相機能不能用來記錄「邊走邊說」的內容。結果攝影機大約拍了 14 分鐘左右，就突然沒電停掉了，所以這支影片並不是完整的散步錄影，而是一次很真實的工具測試。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>20260515自由人生實驗室#004：想拍就拍，不要等待。</title><link>https://garrolan.github.io/garrosolivagant/videos/20260515-004-shoot-without-waiting/</link><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 00:04:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://garrolan.github.io/garrosolivagant/videos/20260515-004-shoot-without-waiting/</guid><description>&lt;div style="position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden;">
 &lt;iframe allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share; fullscreen" loading="eager" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/wjdqbsG9zhg?autoplay=0&amp;amp;controls=1&amp;amp;end=0&amp;amp;loop=0&amp;amp;mute=0&amp;amp;start=0" style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border:0;" title="YouTube video">&lt;/iframe>
 &lt;/div>

&lt;p>這是自由人生實驗室的一次影片創作實驗。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>這次想聊的主題是：想拍就拍，不要等待。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>從一次領夾式麥克風測試失敗、退貨的經驗開始，我重新思考：如果總是等到設備完美、收音完美、腳本完美、狀態完美，很多想法可能就永遠不會被拍下來。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>20260512自由人生實驗室#003：工作不用熱愛，只要幹得來。低敬業者的OFF學。</title><link>https://garrolan.github.io/garrosolivagant/videos/20260512-003-work-without-passion/</link><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 09:03:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://garrolan.github.io/garrosolivagant/videos/20260512-003-work-without-passion/</guid><description>&lt;div style="position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden;">
 &lt;iframe allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share; fullscreen" loading="eager" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/UQg1FROGVJg?autoplay=0&amp;amp;controls=1&amp;amp;end=0&amp;amp;loop=0&amp;amp;mute=0&amp;amp;start=0" style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border:0;" title="YouTube video">&lt;/iframe>
 &lt;/div>

&lt;p>這是自由人生實驗室第 3 支影片，從「低敬業時代」這個概念出發，聊聊我對工作、敬業、加班文化，以及工作生活邊界的想法。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>20260511自由人生實驗室#002：廢話號給我的啟示，低摩擦拍片</title><link>https://garrolan.github.io/garrosolivagant/videos/20260511-002-low-friction-video/</link><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 09:02:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://garrolan.github.io/garrosolivagant/videos/20260511-002-low-friction-video/</guid><description>&lt;div style="position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden;">
 &lt;iframe allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share; fullscreen" loading="eager" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/CSqsXXL3Mns?autoplay=0&amp;amp;controls=1&amp;amp;end=0&amp;amp;loop=0&amp;amp;mute=0&amp;amp;start=0" style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border:0;" title="YouTube video">&lt;/iframe>
 &lt;/div>

&lt;p>這支影片記錄我對低摩擦拍片的想法：與其一開始就追求完整企劃、精緻剪輯和完美封面，不如先讓影片成為自由人生實驗室的一種影像筆記。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>20260511自由人生實驗室#001：先做一個MVP最小可行性產品</title><link>https://garrolan.github.io/garrosolivagant/videos/20260511-001-mvp-video/</link><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 09:01:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://garrolan.github.io/garrosolivagant/videos/20260511-001-mvp-video/</guid><description>&lt;div style="position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden;">
 &lt;iframe allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share; fullscreen" loading="eager" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/LYiOWGcVN4I?autoplay=0&amp;amp;controls=1&amp;amp;end=0&amp;amp;loop=0&amp;amp;mute=0&amp;amp;start=0" style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border:0;" title="YouTube video">&lt;/iframe>
 &lt;/div>

&lt;p>這支影片是自由人生實驗室的第一支影片 MVP。重點不是一開始就完美，而是先用最小成本測試流程，看看自己真正會卡在哪裡。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>